ups now</span><hr size=1> I've seen this since before the last 2 patches, but rarely.  Seems if you do enough damage right at the end, you get xp.  Useing SOS is probably enough of a blast at the very end to do it every time.<br>
<br>
As far as PL, just do what I've done since Lesser Evac was introduced.  Pull to the safe spot, root mob, snare mob, nuke mob to 5%, then evac.  Soon as you zone out, have Powerlevelee kill the mob.  Not sure why, but sometimes they poof when you do this.<br>
